<h2><a id="Bib">Bibliography</a></h2>

<h3>Primary Literature</h3>

<p>
The current standard German edition of Benjamin&rsquo;s work remains
Suhrkamp&rsquo;s seven volume <em>Gesammelte Schriften</em>, edited by
Tiedemann and Schweppenhauser, although a new <em>Kritish
Gesamtausgabe</em>, also by Suhrkamp and projected at twenty-one
volumes, began to appear in 2008 and is due to be completed in 2027.
The standard English edition is Harvard University Press&rsquo; recent
four volume <em>Selected Writings</em>, <em>Early Writings</em>, and
<em>The Arcades Project</em>.</p>

